    "title": "Creating an Article: Main Steps"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When you create an article in Apple News Format, you start by creating a JSON document file. The file contains code that specifies the layout for your article, provides the content, and customizes the look. The file is processed and rendered as an article in Apple News. The following figure shows the basic tasks associated with creating an article.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "media-3975561",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Main-Steps",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Main Steps",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "Before you start, download ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/news-preview/",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": " and follow the instructions to choose the devices you want to preview on. Then, as you create your article, you can drag your ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "article.json",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": " file to the News Preview window to see how your content will look in Apple News.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Note",
          "style": "note",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "text": "Create an",
                          "type": "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type": "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "article.json",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "text": "document file",
                          "type": "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type": "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". All article document files must have the name ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "article.json.",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " Start by adding the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNewsFormat/ArticleDocument",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " object and its required properties, or download this ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/news-publisher/download/Apple_News_Starter_Article.zip",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". You can use any text editor to edit the code in your ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "article.json",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " file. See ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/setting-up-the-introductory-tutorial#Choose-a-Text-Editor",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". Create a unique folder to hold the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "article.json",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " file and any other files you’ll publish with this article, such as image files.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "text": "Plan the layout of your article",
                          "type": "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type": "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". Decide how many layout columns your design needs. See ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/planning-the-layout-for-your-article",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "text": "Add components that contain your article’s content",
                          "type": "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type": "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". The content of your article — the text, photos, and other information — is contained in an array of components in your ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "article.json",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " file. Each component has a specific function — for example, a title, a caption, body text, or a video. For an overview of the different kinds of components you can have in your article, see ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/components",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "; to learn how to add components, see ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/adding-components",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "text": "Position the components in your article",
                          "type": "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type": "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". Use the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNewsFormat/ComponentLayout",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " object to specify where each component will appear horizontally in your article document. See ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/positioning-the-content-in-your-article",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "text": "Customize the appearance of your article",
                          "type": "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type": "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". Include styles, animations, behaviors, and other effects. See ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/enhancing-your-articles-with-styles",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " and ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/about-component-animations",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "inlineContent": [
                        {
                          "text": "Add the metadata for your article",
                          "type": "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type": "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". See ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNewsFormat/Metadata",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Once your article is finished, you can publish it to Apple News. See ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNewsAPI/POST-channels-_channelId_-articles",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "To provide users with the best possible reading experience in Apple News, you must publish the full text of each article. Don’t truncate articles or require users to leave the Apple News app to read the full story.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Important",
          "style": "important",
          "type": "aside"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
